{"id":34615,"date":"2020-12-01T16:40:44","date_gmt":"2020-12-01T12:40:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=34615"},"modified":"2020-12-04T11:44:51","modified_gmt":"2020-12-04T07:44:51","slug":"aisha-when-man-become-vile","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/01\/aisha-when-man-become-vile\/","title":{"rendered":"Aisha on Arrogance: When does a man become a villain?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Muhasibi reported: It was said to Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhen does a man become villainous?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen he thinks of himself as virtuous.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Ri\u2019\u0101yah li-\u1e24uq\u016bq All\u0101h 337<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">\u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0645\u062d\u0627\u0633\u0628\u064a \u0648\u0642\u064a\u0644 \u0644\u0639\u0627\u0626\u0634\u0629 \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u0627 \u0645\u062a\u0649 \u064a\u0643\u0648\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u062c\u0644 \u0645\u0633\u064a\u0626\u0627\u064b \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0625\u0630\u0627 \u0638\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0647 \u0645\u062d\u0633\u0646<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right\">337 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0639\u0627\u064a\u0629 \u0644\u062d\u0642\u0648\u0642 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Al-Muhasibi reported: It was said to Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhen does a man become villainous?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen he thinks of himself as virtuous.\u201d Source: al-Ri\u2019\u0101yah [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3712,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"